{
  "stem": "10829.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If not, you didn't have any.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was type of a life DP camps was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we stayed there till our quota came in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And of course, you were freer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You could go wherever you wanted to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You didn't have to ask for permission to go into the city or ask for permission.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when our quota came, we finally boarded.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we went to New York.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We landed on April the 6th of 1949.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the, the HIAS met us there on the ship.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they picked us up and held us overnight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they-- early in the morning, they put us on a train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or is it that evening they put us on the train?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the 7th I was here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they kept us-- early in the morning, we got off of the ship.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They kept us there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We ate dinner.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put us on a train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We rode all night long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on April the 7th, I think it was about 9 o'clock in the morning, we came in to Columbus, Ohio.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we had to be.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to be in order to-- in order to go, in order to go to Palestine, you had to be an orphan to go and be there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because if you had parents, you could have, then your parents would have had to be with you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The camps that-- the groups that we joined were strictly for orphans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they had different DP camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had different groups where parents and their kids could go and go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But is not-- my sister and I wanted to be in a fighting, a mission-oriented.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was part of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I would say, in retrospect, it was because I was brainwashed by the Haganahs.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
